        "heading": "When to See a Doctor",
        "content": "Consult a doctor if your headache is severe, persistent, recurring, or accompanied by other concerning symptoms. Early medical consultation can prevent complications and ensure proper diagnosis. You can also ask GoDavaii AI for initial guidance before your doctor visit."
